==Project Name==
OVSDB Integration

==Features==
* REST APIs for OVSDB Server Table Management (CRUD)
* Support for OpenStack Neutron L2 Networks API using OpenDaylight Mechanism Driver
* Support for VXLAN and GRE Tunnels for overlay mesh networks

